menu "full_node example"

    config FULL_NODE_WIFI_SSID
        string "Wi-Fi SSID (empty = loopback-only, no radio)"
        default ""
        help
            SSID of the Wi-Fi station to join. Leave empty (the default, and
            what CI builds) to skip Wi-Fi entirely: the node's self-proof runs
            over lwIP's loopback netif. Set it (plus the password) to make the
            node's UDP listener reachable from a real host peer on the LAN.

    config FULL_NODE_WIFI_PASSWORD
        string "Wi-Fi password"
        default ""
        help
            WPA2 password for FULL_NODE_WIFI_SSID. Ignored when the SSID is
            empty.

endmenu
